    <item>
      <title>Work and Corona (WoCo)</title>
      <link>https://fabiankal.github.io/project/woco/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Jul 2021 12:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://fabiankal.github.io/project/woco/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;short-project-description&#34;&gt;Short project description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This project aims to visualize the transformation of work during the COVID-19 pandemic. It cooperates with the Austrian Corona Panel Project and develops survey waves that focus on topics surrounding changes in work itself or work related attitudes and preferences. The main goal of the project is to create a website to provide the public with tools to investigate changes in attitudes, behaviour and preferences themselves via an interactive dashboard.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;publication&#34;&gt;Publication&lt;/h2&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
